{"tid":1047289,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"【終年52歲】《Beverly Hills, 90210》男星 Luke Perry中風逝世","createTime":"2019-03-05T00:31:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-05T11:40:41.000Z","uid":130626,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"d6e0da6f7578e0ca25e296be13cb5d8b7e7b55dd","tid":1047289,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-05T00:31:58.000Z","msg":"Perry上周三在寓所中風，被送入加州洛杉磯一間醫院，延至周一不治。Perry的經理人表示，Perry臨終時前妻Rachel Minnie Sharp、一對子女、未婚妻Wendy Madison Bauer及其他親友陪伴在病榻旁。<br />\nPerry早在80年代入行，90年代憑人氣青春劇《Beverly Hills, 90210》走紅。他在劇中飾演孤單型男Dylan McKay。<br />\nPerry入院前一天，霍士電視台宣佈有意找回《Beverly Hills, 90210》原班人馬重拍6集特輯。<br />\nPerry多年來一直活躍電視圈，也參與過《第五元素》（Fifth Element）等電影的演出，近年亦參演Netflix劇集《河谷鎮》（Riverdale）。<br />\n路透社／英國《每日鏡報》 <br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190305/large/1551722649_df4c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190305%2Flarge%2F1551722649_df4c.jpg&h=4c7db002&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20190305/59330935\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190305%2F59330935&d=aJy3RA7fpCa2KE6CQkcakwjGR3CVFSgRSSfEWrWQqBA%3D&h=ad81fe64\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190305%2F59330935&h=80fff20c\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20190305/59330935</a>"},{"pid":"dfed02ef8dabf47d93d1a8e469674c28ca86b28b","tid":1047289,"uid":227393,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-05T01:00:29.000Z","msg":"幾靚仔<br />\nRIP"},{"pid":"855f6fe0669f28d97a5cbcda0d9092f9f7fbfc7e","tid":1047289,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-05T03:26:59.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4967ef461b26e6c0b6c32fce1c70996911ba3d46","tid":10